<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> haller <del rend="strikethrough">ſe </del>
                        Juſſit ſic </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_61" id="29r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Puspach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>dinst</add> bevor. Lieber <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von solchs wortes und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dehtnüsse</expan> wegen, als ir gen
                                <expan>unsere<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan></add>, <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>burgrafe<ex>n</ex></expan>, und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Aufsesse von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> kumen sein <add>sullt</add> etc., <add>lassen
                            wir ew</add> wissen, <add>daz</add> wir czumal nihts <add>davon
                                    <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan></add>. So
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir auch Herdegen Valczner und Sebolt
                        Pfinczing, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, von den ir uns
                            <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, auch <add>darumb</add> gefragt
                        und die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>,
                        daz <add>in auch</add> niht kunt <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> sey;
                            <add>und</add> wer ez, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>herr<ex>en</ex></expan>, die <expan>burggr<ex>afen</ex></expan>, oder
                        her <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Aufsesz <add>uns</add> darümb icht
                                <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> oder <add>mit</add> uns davon
                                <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>würde<ex>n</ex></expan>, so <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir euch
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz ir
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> sache unschuldig wert.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<add>a</add>t<ex>o</ex></expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan>
<expan>voce<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jocunditat<ex>is</ex></expan> anno viii<hi rend="sup">vo</hi>.
                                <lb/><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> haller jussit sic.</ab>
</div>
